channel.title: MaxxyScape v1 (317)
channel.description:
[b]Intro:[/b] First of all, yes, yes i know, i'm a noob cause i don't have a custom client. I'm still using silab =) But i've currently learning how to make a client, because i'm only familiar with server-sided stuff. But anyways, this is the latest "thing" i've been working on, MaxxyScape, base is NaderPkz v1, so yes, i give 50% or more of the credit to Owner Nader. Thanks for the awesome source! [b]Credits:[/b] Maxxy(Me) = 50% Nader = 50+% [b]Features[/b]
Fully Working Barrows New Home Plenty Of Custom Commands Same ol' Icon Minigame made by Nader New Shops New Staffzone New Skills Area much more...
This is only my v1, so i haven't made many changes. [b]Pictures[/b] [IMG]http://i25.tinypic.com/10hkdac.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i27.tinypic.com/epke1t.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i25.tinypic.com/2ebhgzr.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i25.tinypic.com/11r8b4l.jpg[/img] That's really it! I;ll keep workin on it! Thanks, Maxxy
